God will really build you up in ways unimaginable.. I remember yearssss ago like yearsss I would edit myself before even posting a picture until one day I ask God for motivation and he gave me that PLUS more and I found myself so motivated to be the person I imagined - physically spiritually and mentally.. remember when you ask God for something he will often give the opposite, I asked for motivation and he placed things in my way that I needed to have the motivation for! I’m so happy with me now and that’s all because of God. I was seeking happiness of the world and now I seek happiness from him and him only and the has caused me to love who he made me to be endlessly.

Crazy to think it’s been a year straight since I started working out every single day , if not 6 days a week. In the beginning it was hard, but overtime your spirit truly gets accustomed to a certain routine and no matter what it becomes a lifestyle. Find classes you like, places you like to eat and cute places to inspire you. & as content creators we spend most of our time outside or inside so it’s important to have a routine to keep us sane 💕
The only difference between you and where you want to be is consistency.

As I near 4 months in New York City, I can finally see what God has been preparing me for. In the beginning it wasn’t easy, and to be honest it still isn’t, as a person who doesn’t like change much but constantly steps out on change to fix that issue this shift to New York has been interesting. Seeing the blessings God has provided for me here while letting go of what was. “ forget the former things, do not dwell on the past “ has been my constant reminder to allow God to work his perfect work.

Missing my mark is something i think about daily.. i never want to wake up one day and I didn’t do the things that my heart desired.. the older you get you realize life is truly about the still moments , the moments you came to realization, the moments you found out your boundaries, your non negotiables, those moments.. I strive daily to learn myself more and more , to get to know me because truly I change everyday and I’m never the same person not even to myself .. and it takes time getting to know her again.. this new me loves fitness, she loves church, she loves self dates, she loves hosting, she loves so much things .. and I never wanna miss my mark on her

#lifestyle #luxurylifestyle #lifelessons #inspiration #showerroutine #showerthoughts

When I think about dating, relationships and even marriage I realize as much as we as humans yearn for it , I’ve truly gotten to a place of allowing God to truly bring that man to me. I can fully say I’m not looking, I’m not chasing, frankly I’m so free it’s insane lol by choice .. most times we let those moments of alone make us think we’re alone , I’m here to remind you that just because you’re lonely doesn’t mean you’re alone. When you’re someone who wants something valuable and long lasting you truly don’t seek out just anything.. allow God to work his magic.. I’ve never been someone to go out of my way, God knows me and he knows exactly the way my attention needs to be kept lol and until then.. may life continue to be joyful 

#dating #datingadvice #christian #christianrelationships #christainlife #marriage #single #relationships
